{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e85fef4101","title":"中共沿河县委对张艰珍所犯错误的处分报告","origin":"贵州省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"def6e3ddf7","index":0,"year":1961,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"e85fef4101"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2ae3f3778b","type":"title","text":"中共沿河县委对张艰珍所犯错误的处分报告","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"be2746449b","type":"paragraph","text":"张艰珍，男，34岁，家庭中农成分，原任黑水高穴管理区总支书，现已撤职任工作员。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"8c0232ee7c","type":"paragraph","text":"主要错误事实如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"f9eff29210","type":"paragraph","text":"一、逼死人命三条。（1）59年冬，崔道亨，田树华，崔照法，被张诬认杀牛，被他吊打关押五天，三人即死。（2）59年冬，抽崔道浪到岗岭挖蕨巴根，因回队背柴，被艰珍发觉吊一天。（3）59年冬，队里猪死，崔德中，崔德良去烫猪，艰珍诬认德良杀死，将德良吊到大平队，又60年，艰珍与张献武伙同主张，将崔光艰，崔光扬等9人弄在大平集训，罚苦工20天。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"9aea7cf85b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、59年春至同年8月，艰珍亲带队干青年，在大平队先后翻箱倒柜52次，达134户，所翻出粮食、油、肉、菜及生活小用具，全被拿走，在崔德林家翻得三斤猪油和油罐都拿走了。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"60a03946d9","type":"paragraph","text":"三、贪污队和食堂的猪、牛肉61斤，大米86斤，蜂糖22斤半，币76元5角。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"d85d6b258f","type":"appellation","text":"四、冒领和扣粮油：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"2ca7b4a765","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）干堡小队食堂实有吃饭的42人，假报77人，冒领35人的粮油和小队干部袁翠英，崔照武，崔柄光私分了。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"},{"id":"6ea804889f","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）60年2月，规定每人每天吃四两粮，有四天艰珍就发2两粮，克扣自吞。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101"}],"page":{"id":"ae091298b4","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"e85fef4101","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}